# HolisticTechAgency Project Context

## Project Overview
A React-based webpage for HolisticTechAgency built with Vite.

## Project Structure
```
src/
├─ App.jsx          # Main application component
├─ main.jsx         # Application entry point
├─ components/
│  └─ Header.jsx    # Header component with styled first letters
├─ assets/
│  └─ icons/
│     ├─ favicon-light.svg
│     └─ favicon-dark.svg
└─ styles/
   └─ themes.css    # CSS theme constants and styles
```

## Key Components
- App.jsx: Main application component with CSS-based theme styling
- main.jsx: Application entry point that imports CSS and renders App
- Header.jsx: Header component displaying "HOLISTIC TECH AGENCY" with styled first letters
- themes.css: CSS file with theme constants, color palette, and media queries for light/dark themes
- index.html: HTML template with inline FOUC prevention styles, script, and responsive favicons
- favicon-light.svg: Light theme favicon
- favicon-dark.svg: Dark theme favicon

## Key Variables and Methods
- CSS Custom Properties: --bg-color, --text-color, --font-primary, --font-heading
- Color Palette: --color-primary (#923a26), --color-secondary (#eccd0f), --color-tertiary (#dbc8a0), --color-accent (#e07e00)
- Inverted Colors: --color-primary-invert (#6dc5d9), --color-secondary-invert (#1332f0), --color-tertiary-invert (#24375f), --color-accent-invert (#1f81ff)
- Media Query: @media (prefers-color-scheme: dark) for automatic theme detection
- Header Component: Displays "HOLISTIC TECH AGENCY" with first letters styled in different colors

## CSS Theme Constants
- --bg-color: Background color (white for light theme, black for dark theme)
- --text-color: Text color (black for light theme, white for dark theme)
- --font-primary: Primary font family (Helvetica Neue, sans-serif)
- --font-heading: Heading font family (Helvetica, sans-serif)

## Notes
- Minimal design approach - functionality first
- No styling other than layout and size purposes
- Test after each step by running the app